item.title: CVE-2022-4546|2024-08-03T01:41:45.607Z -- unknown -- mapwiz
item.description: The Mapwiz WordPress plugin through 1.0.1 does not properly sanitise and escape a parameter before using it in a SQL statement, leading to a SQL injection exploitable by high privilege users such as admin.
